  },
  "customHelp": "Green = Harvester (gather energy). Red = Reaper (hunt). When you PLAY a Reaper or Harvester it enters HOME (Just Played). At DUSK (end of your turn) ALL your cards slide to HOME (Can Invade) — from there they may push into TO INVADE (the opponent's area) on a later turn. So: Just Played = this turn's plays only; everything graduates right at Dusk. COUNTERS in order: Energy | Balance. ENERGY = your spendable pool this turn (Raw + Life merged into one to cut clicks) — gain it at Dawn, spend it, convert leftover to Population at Dusk. BALANCE = your score. POPULATION = red pips placed on your Harvesters (this is what accumulates). Treachery = drag the red marker along the 1-10 track (starts on 5). Play 1 Creator from your Creator Deck pile at start of turn. Tokens: black = Death, red pip = Population.",
